Florida Beats Brigham Young, Connecticut Defeats San Diego State in NCAA

-- B y   D e x   M c L u s k e y
-- 
2011-03-25T01:40:53Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-25/florida-beats-brigham-young-connecticut-defeats-san-diego-state-in-ncaa.html
The University of Florida beat
Brigham Young University 83-74 in overtime in college
basketball’s national men’s championship.  The second-ranked Gators advance to a meeting with Butler
or  Wisconsin  in the Southeast Regional final at the National
Collegiate Athletic Association tournament.  Also tonight, the University of  Connecticut  beat San Diego
State University 74-67 to advance to a meeting with defending
champion and No. 1 seed Duke or fifth-ranked  Arizona  in the West
Regional final.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Dex McLuskey at 
 dmcluskey@bloomberg.net  